:

1. *Pobrini* se da svi budu na vreme! (Take care that everyone is on time!)
2. On se *pobrinuo* da svi budu tu. (He took care that everyone was there.)
3. Ona će se *pobrinuti* da svi budu zadovoljni. (She will take care that everyone is satisfied.)
4. Ne brini, ja ću se *pobrinuti* za sve. (Don't worry, I will take care of everything.)
5. On je već *pobrinuo* se za sve. (He has already taken care of everything.)